00:15:49.980 --> 00:15:52.080
about when you see this.

00:15:52.080 --> 00:15:53.970
And what's particularly
interesting

00:15:53.970 --> 00:15:56.890
is how when you look
at people's responses

00:15:56.890 --> 00:16:01.440
